'''Origen ESP''' is the sister team of [[Origen]] and was built to compete in the Spanish scene.

== History ==
'''Origen ESP''' was created by the [[Origen]] organization in January 2017 to compete in the [[LVP SuperLiga Orange/Season 12|LVP SuperLiga Orange Season 12]].

